caption.p: Dendrogram of chemical data from miscellaneous taxa in Prostanthera, not part of the P. ovalifolia or P. rotundiolia group. CES = P. centralis, SUS = P. suborbicularis, STA = P. striatiflora, MNF = P. sp. Minyon Falls, OSF = P. sp. Olney State Forest, CUA = P. cuneata, PRS = P. prunelloides, LIS = P. lithospermoides, RIS = P. ringens, INA = P. incisa, CAA = P. caerulea, BGB = P. sp. Baking Board, TOR = P. sp. Thredbo River, GRR, P. sp. Gibraltar Range, ASS = P. aspalathoides, PIA = P. sp. Piliga, and DAC = P. sp. Dandarha Creek.
